Purchase Features:
    • Configuration:
        ◦ Set up purchase-related configurations.
    • Products:
        ◦ Manage product-related configurations for purchases.
    • Product Attributes:
        ◦ Define attributes for purchase products.
    • Product Categories:
        ◦ Categorize products for organized purchasing.
    • Settings:
        ◦ Configure general purchase-related settings.
    • Units of Measures:
        ◦ Define different units of measure for purchase products.
    • Units of Measure Categories:
        ◦ Categorize units of measure for organized tracking.
    • Vendor Pricelists:
        ◦ Manage pricelists for different vendors.
    • Orders:
        ◦ Manage purchase orders and requests for quotation.
    • Vendors:
        ◦ Manage and organize vendor details.
    • Products:
        ◦ Manage product variants and individual products for purchases.
    • Reporting:
        ◦ Generate reports related to purchases.
